<p class="MsoBodyText">“Where is the next world inhabited by
bluefaces?”</p>
<p class="MsoBodyText">“According to a book I studied, about twenty
lightyears hence. Wersgorixan itself, the capital planet, is much
farther off than that-farther away than Terra, even.”</p>
<p class="MsoBodyText">“But the far-speaker would inform their
emperor at once of what’s happened, would it not?” asked Captain
Bullard.</p>
<p class="MsoBodyText">“No,” I said. “The far-speaker acts only as
