this. D’you understand? She’s not in her right mind. Some fiend has
possessed her.”</p>
<p class="MsoBodyText">I regarded him with a pity still greater
than before. “You’re too brave to hide behind such foolishness,” I
said.</p>
<p class="MsoBodyText">“Well, what can I do?” he growled.</p>
<p class="MsoBodyText">“You can fight on-“</p>
<p class="MsoBodyText">“Hopelessly, once Montbelle has gone to
