in black velvet, but jewels flashed on the hand which covered a
fire-gun laid in front of him. Lady Catherine wore a gray gown and
wimple. She had overlooked a stray lock of hair, which fell across
her brow like smoldering fire.</p>
<p class="MsoBodyText">Sir Roger halted just within the cabin door.
